creator: Paxum Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Paxum is a Canadian Payment Service Provider providing low-cost way for Business to pay their invoices to affiliates and publishers worldwide.

Payout options include:
-Wires via SWIFT to over 200 countries
- External Card Loads (OCT Transfers) to any Visa or Mastercard
- EFT Transfers (Local bank transfers in local currencies). Over 100 Countries supported
- Prepaid Debit Cards

Personalized IBAN Account
-Paxum also offers clients worldwide a free EUR IBAN account for all incoming payments via SEPA.

Push Notifications
- Your account activity is completely transparent due to push notifications that you will receive on your mobile phone.

Security
- We use latest encryption technology to guarantee you 100% protection and peace of mind.

Paxum is the preferred global payment method for content creators, affiliates, publishers, advertising networks, freelance professionals and more. If you already use Paxum then it makes sense to download the Paxum App so you can securely and efficiently manage your Paxum global payment account from your Android Smartphone.

Both Personal and Business users can use the Paxum App to:
Send Money
Get Instant Notifications when Funds are Received
Withdraw Funds
Transfer Funds
Convert Funds
View Recent Transactions
View Balance in Real Time
And More...

It’s easy to take Paxum everywhere you go with the user-friendly, secure and elegantly designed Paxum App. Download the Paxum App today and discover the convenience and beauty of easy on-the-go payments!
